item.description:
Millwood Farms - 9 holes after work on Thursday.

These twilight rounds are a great way to get some practice in during the week. If you are a relative beginner or have only been playing a few years, this is a great way to learn out on the course instead of just the range. But regardless of skill level, it's still a great way to practice.

Twilight rate is $12

http://millwoodgolfcourse.com/rates.html
